SUMMARY:Free Yoga Practice
DESCRIPTION:Iama Embodied Community\n🌀 **Move with intention. Connect w
 ith your body. Celebrate community.**\n\nJoin us every **Thursday at 6 PM*
 * for an embodied yoga practice designed to help you release tension\, gro
 und yourself\, and cultivate presence. This is a trauma-informed\, all-lev
 els class\, no prior yoga experience needed. Expect a Hatha-Vinyasa flow\,
  breathwork\, and a space to listen to your body’s wisdom.\n\n🌿 **Eve
 ry last Thursday of the month\, stay after class for a community potluck d
 inner!**\n\n📍 **Location**: 727 T St. Sacramento CA 95811\n✨ **All ou
 r events are free. Donations are welcome.**\n📩 **Questions? Reach out a
 t** embody.iama@gmail.com\n🔗 **Follow us on Instagram:** [@embody.iama]
 (https://www.instagram.com/embody.iama)
