SUMMARY:Yolo Wine Ramble
DESCRIPTION:Ramble around Yolo County’s wine country & discover the wine country you didn’t know you were missing! Ramble around the county exploring all of Yolo’s wine trail and incredible wineries. \nApril 25th & 26th \nWith our Wine Ramble tickets\, you and a friend get buy one\, get one wine flight (BOGO) all weekend long! Sip\, Savor\, and stay the weekend with our association wineries. Our 14 participating members are family-owned\, estate-grown and award-winning. Ramble weekend details are below – create your own ramble itinerary or use our suggested Yolo wine trails!
